title: AI Supply Chain Mermaid Diagram
tags: [[GettingStarted]] [[AI Supply Chain]] [[Flowcharts]]
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki.mermaid

flowchart TD

%% =========================
%% DEMAND / END MARKETS
%% =========================

Users[Users / Enterprises / Governments]
Apps[AI Applications<br/>Assistants, coding, search, agents, robotics, ads, defense, drug discovery]
APIs[Model APIs / SaaS Platforms]
Inference[Inference Serving]
Training[Pretraining / Fine-tuning / RLHF / Evaluation]
Models[Foundation Models]

Users --> Apps --> APIs --> Inference --> Models
Training --> Models
Models --> Inference

%% =========================
%% MODEL INPUTS
%% =========================

Data[Training / Evaluation Data]
HumanData[Human preference data<br/>RLHF, labeling, expert feedback]
SyntheticData[Synthetic data]
EnterpriseData[Enterprise / private data]
OpenData[Public web / code / papers]
LicensedData[Licensed data]

OpenData --> Data
LicensedData --> Data
EnterpriseData --> Data
SyntheticData --> Data
HumanData --> Training
Data --> Training

Algorithms[Algorithms / Architectures<br/>Transformers, MoE, diffusion, retrieval, agents]
MLTalent[Researchers / ML Engineers]
EvalSafety[Evaluation / Safety / Red teaming]

Algorithms --> Training
MLTalent --> Training
EvalSafety --> Models
EvalSafety --> Apps

%% =========================
%% SOFTWARE STACK
%% =========================

Frameworks[ML Frameworks<br/>PyTorch, JAX, TensorFlow, Triton]
Compilers[Compilers / Runtime<br/>CUDA, ROCm, XLA, TensorRT, vLLM-like serving]
Kernels[GPU Kernels / Collective Communication]
Schedulers[Cluster Schedulers / Orchestration]
Observability[Monitoring / Logging / Security]
VectorDB[Vector DB / Retrieval / Embeddings]

Frameworks --> Training
Frameworks --> Inference
Compilers --> Frameworks
Kernels --> Compilers
Schedulers --> Training
Schedulers --> Inference
Observability --> Apps
VectorDB --> Apps
EnterpriseData --> VectorDB

%% =========================
%% COMPUTE CLUSTER
%% =========================

ComputeCluster[AI Compute Cluster]
Servers[AI Servers]
Accelerators[AI Accelerators<br/>GPU / TPU / ASIC]
CPUs[CPUs]
HBM[High-Bandwidth Memory]
DRAM[Server DRAM]
Storage[NVMe SSD / HDD Storage]
Networking[Networking Fabric<br/>InfiniBand / Ethernet / Optical]
NICs[NICs / DPUs]
Switches[Switch ASICs / Switch Systems]
Optics[Optical Transceivers / Lasers]
Racks[Racks / Power Shelves / Cabling]

ComputeCluster --> Training
ComputeCluster --> Inference
Servers --> ComputeCluster
Accelerators --> Servers
CPUs --> Servers
HBM --> Accelerators
DRAM --> Servers
Storage --> ComputeCluster
Networking --> ComputeCluster
NICs --> Networking
Switches --> Networking
Optics --> Networking
Racks --> Servers

%% =========================
%% CHIP DESIGN
%% =========================

ChipDesign[Chip Design]
EDA[EDA Software]
IP[Semiconductor IP<br/>CPU, SerDes, memory controllers, interconnect]
Firmware[Firmware / Drivers]
DesignTalent[Chip Architects / Verification Engineers]

EDA --> ChipDesign
IP --> ChipDesign
DesignTalent --> ChipDesign
Firmware --> Accelerators
ChipDesign --> Accelerators
ChipDesign --> CPUs
ChipDesign --> NICs
ChipDesign --> Switches

%% =========================
%% SEMICONDUCTOR MANUFACTURING
%% =========================

Foundry[Foundry / Logic Wafer Fab]
MemoryFab[Memory Fabs]
Wafer[Silicon Wafers]
Lithography[Lithography Tools<br/>EUV / DUV]
SemiTools[Semicap Equipment<br/>Etch, deposition, metrology, inspection, cleaning]
Photoresist[Photoresists]
Gases[Specialty Gases]
Chemicals[Wet Chemicals / Slurries]
UPW[Ultrapure Water]
Masks[Photomasks]
Yield[Process Yield / Metrology]

ChipDesign --> Foundry
Foundry --> Accelerators
Foundry --> CPUs
Foundry --> NICs
Foundry --> Switches

MemoryFab --> HBM
MemoryFab --> DRAM
MemoryFab --> Storage

Wafer --> Foundry
Wafer --> MemoryFab
Lithography --> Foundry
Lithography --> MemoryFab
SemiTools --> Foundry
SemiTools --> MemoryFab
Photoresist --> Foundry
Gases --> Foundry
Chemicals --> Foundry
UPW --> Foundry
Masks --> Foundry
Yield --> Foundry
Yield --> MemoryFab

%% =========================
%% ADVANCED PACKAGING
%% =========================

AdvancedPackaging[Advanced Packaging<br/>CoWoS-like 2.5D, interposers, chiplets]
Substrates[ABF / Advanced Package Substrates]
Interposers[Silicon Interposers / Bridges]
Test[Wafer Sort / Final Test / Burn-in]
OSAT[OSAT / Assembly Providers]

Foundry --> AdvancedPackaging
HBM --> AdvancedPackaging
Substrates --> AdvancedPackaging
Interposers --> AdvancedPackaging
OSAT --> AdvancedPackaging
AdvancedPackaging --> Accelerators
Test --> Accelerators

%% =========================
%% DATA CENTER
%% =========================

DataCenter[AI Data Center]
Land[Land / Zoning / Permits]
Construction[Construction / EPC]
PowerInfra[Electrical Infrastructure<br/>Substations, transformers, switchgear, PDUs, UPS]
Cooling[Cooling<br/>Air, direct-to-chip liquid, chillers, heat rejection]
Water[Water / Coolant / Heat Reuse]
Fiber[Fiber Backhaul / Internet Exchanges]
Security[Physical Security / Operations]
Backup[Backup Power<br/>Batteries, diesel, gas turbines]

DataCenter --> ComputeCluster
Land --> DataCenter
Construction --> DataCenter
PowerInfra --> DataCenter
Cooling --> DataCenter
Water --> Cooling
Fiber --> DataCenter
Security --> DataCenter
Backup --> DataCenter

%% =========================
%% ENERGY
%% =========================

Grid[Electric Grid]
Generation[Power Generation<br/>Gas, nuclear, renewables, hydro]
Transmission[Transmission Lines]
Interconnect[Grid Interconnection Queue]
Transformers[Large Transformers]
Switchgear[Switchgear / Breakers]
PPAs[Power Purchase Agreements]
GasSupply[Natural Gas Supply]
Uranium[Uranium / Nuclear Fuel]
SolarWind[Solar / Wind Equipment]
Batteries[Grid Batteries]

Generation --> Grid
Transmission --> Grid
Grid --> PowerInfra
Interconnect --> DataCenter
Transformers --> PowerInfra
Switchgear --> PowerInfra
PPAs --> DataCenter
GasSupply --> Generation
Uranium --> Generation
SolarWind --> Generation
Batteries --> Grid

